1465360/extras/719bac9dc56e18a054fb960940841cfb.avif?t=1773915366\" width=1560 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465360/extras/14ddacb9fe459e7394e11b735325c100.poster.avif?t=1773915366\" width=1140 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465360/extras/14ddacb9fe459e7394e11b735325c100.webm?t=1773915366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1465360/extras/14ddacb9fe459e7394e11b735325c100.mp4?t=1773915366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Drive 40 vehicles from brands such as Ford, Chevrolet, and Freightliner as you leave your mark on an untamed open world. Expand and customize your fleet with many upgrades and accessories including an exhaust snorkel for heavy waters or chain tires to battle the snow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
